SUB_W19_WRLD_MIDO_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_00.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_WRLD_MIDO_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_00.text:
Holy moly, look at all the life in this place!
I'm gonna find plenty of spirit power here,
believe you me.

SUB_W19_WRLD_MIDO_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_01.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_WRLD_MIDO_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_01.text:
Vines... Waterfalls... Yep, this place is
really something. Wonder if I can find
somebody to show me around, maybe.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_000.text:
Got a big old bird starin' right at me!
I bet it'll come after me the moment
I decide to look away.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_010.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_010.text:
Okay, now it's lowering its head...
That means it's not gonna eat me?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_020.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_000_020.text:
Gosh, seems like it wants me to climb
up on its back. ...Eh, what the heck.
Let's give it a shot!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_000.text:
Who'd have thought there'd be such
a huge world on top of a single tree?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_010.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_010.text:
Got a big ol' bear statue over there.
Wonder who made it?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_020.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_010_020.text:
Also got a turtle, a bat, a squirrel...
Oh, I get it now! These aren't statues,
they're petrified animals! THAT'S what
the bird wanted me to see.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_000.text:
Guess I should try to save
those petrified critters, eh?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_020.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_020.text:
Whatcha got for me there, fella?
Looks like...seeds, bugs, and a flute?
Guessin' I use the flute to call
when I need you, yeah?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_040.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_040.text: As for the seeds and bugs...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_080.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_000_CUT_020_080.text:
Maybe I should head to
that viny area over there.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_010_CUT_000_010.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_010_CUT_000_010.text: Don't worry, I'll work this out.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_000_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_000_000.text: Bet I can climb those vines.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_010_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_010_000.text:
Okey-dokey. Now I know I can
climb up using vines.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_010_010.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_010_010.text:
Not sure about the whole 'down' bit,
but I'll figure it out.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_020_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_020_000.text:
Holy smokes, look at that!
Those bugs I got earlier are
chewing through the vines.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_000.text:
The vines turned into a waterfall
and I slid down it.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_010.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_010.text:
Guess that means I can use waterfalls
to move from above to below.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_020.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_020.text:
So the bug can turn vines into a waterfall?
That's one wild critter right there!
But I don't have unlimited bugs,
so better save 'em for when I need 'em.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_030.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_030.text:
So if vines go up and waterfalls
go down, what are the seeds for?

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_040.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_040.text:
Maybe they turn waterfalls into vines?
Let's give it a shot.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_060.speaker: _NOT_SPECIFIED_
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_060.text: Take a stick from the beaver's lodge!

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_070.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_000_CUT_030_070.text:
Holy heck, it's like a voice calling
down from on high! I know better
than to ignore that kind of thing.

SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_099_CUT_000_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_GIMK_MIDO_IVY_099_CUT_000_000.text:
Yeah, I don't think this is where
I oughta be right now.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_BEAVER_000_CUT_000_010.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_BEAVER_000_CUT_000_010.text:
Mind lending me one of your
sticks here? Appreciate it, bud.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_000.text:
Okay, brought back a stick from Mr. Beaver.
I'm guessing that shows you I've figured out
how to get around with vines and waterfalls,
and also how to use bugs and seeds.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_020.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_020.text:
Now those petrified animals are a whole
other...uh, animal, but I'll sure as heck
do whatever I can.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_040.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_040.text:
Say, now that I think about it, wouldn't
it be a lot faster just to fly me around
on your back while I do all this stuff?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_060.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_060.text:
...No dice, eh? Can't say it makes much
sense to me, but this isn't my first
rodeo—I know every world's got its
rules, and I'm gonna make this work.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_080.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_EAGLE_020_CUT_000_080.text:
But lemme ask you something here fella:
you know about any spirits in this world?
'Cause that's why I came here.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_TURTLE_PUSHES_TREE_CUT.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_TURTLE_PUSHES_TREE_CUT.text:
When I saved Mr. Turtle, he said
he'd lend me some of his strength.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_TURTLE_PUSHES_TREE_CUT.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_TURTLE_PUSHES_TREE_CUT.text:
Maybe I'm strong enough to knock
a tree down now? Let's see!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.text:
If only I had some way
to bring this tree down...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.text:
What's that, Mr. Beaver? You're gonna
gnaw that trunk down for me? Well heck,
that oughta do the trick.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_BEAVER_CUTS_TREE_CUT_0.text:
Now I just need to give
it one good shove!

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_CHANGE_CASCADE_TO_IVY_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_CHANGE_CASCADE_TO_IVY_.text: Ah geez, I'm down to my last seed.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_CHANGE_CASCADE_TO_IVY_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_CHANGE_CASCADE_TO_IVY_.text: Let's turn this waterfall into vines.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_CHANGE_IVY_TO_CASCADE_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_CHANGE_IVY_TO_CASCADE_.text: Ah geez, I'm down to my last bug.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_CHANGE_IVY_TO_CASCADE_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_CHANGE_IVY_TO_CASCADE_.text: Let's turn these vines into a waterfall.

SUB_W19_WRLD_MIDO_EAGLE_WHISTLE_GAMEEND_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_WRLD_MIDO_EAGLE_WHISTLE_GAMEEND_.text:
I got all the petrified critters
un-petrified, so that's good.

SUB_W19_WRLD_MIDO_EAGLE_WHISTLE_GAMEEND_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_WRLD_MIDO_EAGLE_WHISTLE_GAMEEND_.text:
Maybe I should look
around a little more.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.text:
Looks like I was able to save
all the petrified critters.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.text:
Guess I oughta head on
back to Mr. Eagle?

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_ALL_GUARDIANS_SAVED_CU.text:
All that's left is to pick up
some spirit power.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.text:
Now that I've got my spirit power sorted,
so I guess it's time to head back. But there
are still some petrified animals left, so...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.text:
Sorry guy, but I got what I came
for and I'm heading back.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_WORLDEXIT_000_CUT_000_.text: So long, bud! It's been fun!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_00.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_00.text:
I somehow managed to
save all the critters.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_02.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_02.text:
Kinda strange that they only got saved
because some guy from another world
came here. Really goes to show that
no world stands completely apart.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_03.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_03.text:
Well, this is goodbye.
Have a good life, Mr. Eagle!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_05.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_000_CUT_000_05.text:
Gosh, I never did figure out how those
animals got petrified in the first place.
I mean, who the heck would do that?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_000_05.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_000_05.text:
Well, that's a scary voice you're
puttin' on right there, Mr. Eagle.
What seems to be the trouble?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_00.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_00.text:
Yikes! Mr. Eagle turned to stone!
Is this what's going on with the
whole petrification deal?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_01.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_01.text:
And I can't save him, neither...
Guess that's a job for someone else?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_02.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_02.text:
Things turn to stone, things turn from stone...
The cycle this world shares with others is
pushing it forward little by little—or at
least that's what I'd like to believe.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_03.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_100_CUT_010_03.text:
Aw, everyone came down to see me off.
So long, folks! Be well!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_02.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_02.text:
Well, hey there, Mr. Bear!
You sure do look scary today.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_04.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_04.text:
You hungry or something there,
Mrs. Squirrel?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_06.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_06.text:
Yeowch! Those piercing shrieks of yours
are hurtin' my ears, Mr. Bat!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_08.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_08.text:
Well, shoot. Even Mr. Turtle
here's angry?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_10.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_000_10.text: And last is you, Mr. Eagle.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_00.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_00.text:
All the defeated animals have turned
to stone. Gotta say, I don't get the
point of fighting like this at all.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_01.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_01.text:
'Course, just because I don't understand it
doesn't mean it's not serving an important
purpose in this here world.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_02.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_200_CUT_010_02.text:
I guess this is goodbye.
Good luck, everybody.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_300_CUT_000_02.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_300_CUT_000_02.text:
Now hold on just a minute! What's everyone
all so hot and bothered about? I mean,
all I did was save your shootin' lives!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_300_CUT_010_00.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_300_CUT_010_00.text:
And now they've all turned back to stone—
including Mr. Eagle. So what's that mean for
the future of this world? I mean, heck, was
everything I did here completely pointless?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_300_CUT_010_01.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GAMEEND_300_CUT_010_01.text:
I could spin on this until I turn blue, but it's
never gonna make sense. Guess all you poor
folks will have to wait until someone else
swings by to unpetrify you again.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.text: The pose of Mrs. Squirrel here...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.text:
Looks like she's about to chow down
on something. A seed? A walnut?
Some kind of fruit, maybe?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_STO.text:
I wonder if she'll go back to normal
if I bring it the right food?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_CUT.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_CUT.text: Yep. It was a walnut, all right.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.text:
Gosh, this is a big fella right here!
First thing that grabbed my attention
when I was looking down from the sky.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.text:
But even though he's stone, the way his
mouth is wide open gives me the willies.
Am I sure I wanna save this fella?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_STO.text:
Hm? This poor guy's missing some teeth.
Maybe that's what I ought to be looking
for here.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_CUT.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_CUT.text:
Still, seeing as it didn't attack me,
I guess he knows I saved him.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_CUT.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_07_CUT.text:
Still, maybe ease back on all the
shoutin' there, fella. You're gonna
give me a heart attack over here.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.text:
I guess this is a bat—but without wings,
the fella looks pretty sad. Better see
if I can get out there and find 'em.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.text:
Wait, is that a walnut in its mouth?
Pretty sure bats don't eat those.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.text:
Well, shoot! Even the walnut's stone.
I can't get it outta there.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_STONE.text:
Guess I'll have to rescue
this poor bat fella first.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.text:
There we go! One set of wings,
just like nature intended.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.text:
Think you can give me that
walnut now, bud? Thanks.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_NEST_02_CUT_0.text: Now I can go save Mrs. Squirrel.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_STON.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_STON.text:
Mr. Turtle here's been turned to stone.
Unless he was like this all along?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_STON.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_STON.text:
Looks like he's missing a piece of shell.
Maybe it broke after it was turned to stone?
...Or did he turn to stone AFTER it broke? Well, I won't solve anything just
standing around here like a dope.
Time to find the missing piece.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.text:
You're not made of stone anymore, right,
Mr. Turtle? You're a pretty slow fella,
so it's a bit hard to tell.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.text:
There we are!
Not stone. Swell.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_SWAMP_06_CUT_.text:
...How's that? You wanna thank me by helping
me out? Well, that's kind of you to offer.
Really appreciate it there, guy.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.text:
Gosh, look at the huge frog. Looks like
it's trying to eat something, maybe?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.text: Well, lookee there! A bat wing!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_C.text:
That was a real close shave,
but I managed to get the bat wing
before Mr. Frog there could eat it.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_A.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_A.text:
That giant frog looks hungry
as anything, believe you me.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_A.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_01_ROUTE2_A.text:
You sure are a scary one,
Mr. Frog.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_02_CUT_000_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_02_CUT_000_.text:
These look like the bones of an animal—
oh, and some of the teeth fell out!
I wonder if these might fit Mr. Bear.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_02_EARLY_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_02_EARLY_CU.text:
These look like the bones of an animal—
got some real nice teeth here, too.
Maybe I'll just hang onto 'em.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_000_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_000_.text:
Yikes, but it was a bad idea to
get close to a snake like that.
Now it's in full-on attack mode!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_000_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_000_.text:
Seems to be guarding some eggs,
but I don't think that's a thing
snakes usually do.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_010_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_010_.text:
Well, heck! Those were birds' eggs!
Weren't babies at all—they were lunch!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_03_CUT_010_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.text:
Yikes! That's a real scary-looking
croc there—and it looks like I
interrupted his lunch.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_04_CUT_000_.text:
Phew! Sure glad I was able to get that
bat wing away from Mr. Croc before
it went down the hatch.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.text:
That beaver's building himself a house!
Fella probably wouldn't mind if I just
stopped and watch him work, eh?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.text:
Cripes, something's got Mr. Beaver in
its sights! Well, nothing for it but to sit
back and let nature take its course.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.text:
I know that poor fella was just looking
to score its first meal in who knows
how long, but I couldn't help myself.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_05_ROUTE2_C.text:
...What's that, Mr. Beaver?
You got something to thank me with?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_C.text:
Gosh, even the dragonflies are huge.
One of the fruits of all the spirit
power here, I suppose.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_C.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_C.text:
Doesn't look like it'll come after me,
but to a little bug, that thing must seem
like one ferocious hunter. I mean, heck,
even I'm scared of those eyes!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_E.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_E.text:
I wonder if dragonflies are territorial?
Sure'd be nice if they could all manage
to get along, but...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_E.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_SWAMP_06_ROUTE2_E.text: Oh! Looks like they're getting along plenty well. Must be a male and female. ...Kinda jealous, if I'm bein' honest.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.text:
Cripes almighty, that is one huge spider!
Let's see if I can just slip past here...

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.text:
Dang it! Thing spotted me!
I gotta protect the ant.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_01_AUTO_CUT_.text: Boy, that was close. So the spider was after us, huh? Scary.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_01_ROUTE2_AU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_01_ROUTE2_AU.text:
The jig's up!
Gotta protect the dragonfly!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_CUT_000_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_CUT_000_0.text:
Well, we finally made it to the anthill.
Why were you journeying so far from home,
fella? I mean, I enjoy an adventure as much
as the next guy, but safety first, eh?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.text:
There's a walnut in that anthill.
That's gotta be Mrs. Squirrel's chow.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.text:
Let's see if I can take it without
getting these ants all feisty.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.text:
What's going on there, Mr. Ant?
Something I can help you with?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.text:
You must've climbed up here, yeah?
'Cause you sure don't look like
you're from around here.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_CUT_000_0.text:
Well, I can't promise we'll find your hill,
but maybe we get lucky if we stick together.
Us travelers all gotta look out for each
other, after all!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_CU.text:
Now that is one big ant.
Thought you were a spider there, guy!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_CU.text:
Oh hey, looks like it's carrying some kind
of seed. Wonder if I can find food for that
squirrel in its anthill, maybe?

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.text:
Think those bees would mind
me borrowing a little honey
from their hive?

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.text:
Gya! They're coming straight for me!
The bees here can read minds!

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_AUTO_CUT_.text:
Well, that's enough of that.
Time to head on outta here.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_ROUTE2_CU.text:
A dragonfly just came soaring
from that beehive!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_ROUTE2_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_05_ROUTE2_CU.text:
Say, I seem to remember seeing a big
dragonfly back in that swamp area.
What say we swing by and check it out?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_06_CUT_000_0.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_06_CUT_000_0.text:
There's a bat wing caught
in that spiderweb there!

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_06_ROUTE2_AU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_06_ROUTE2_AU.text:
There's a dragonfly in that web!
Better save him before he's lunch.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_06_ROUTE2_AU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_06_ROUTE2_AU.text:
You all right there, Mr. Dragonfly?
You got a whole lot of eyes, so I'd
expect you to be more careful.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.text:
Aw, look at those wolf pups playing!
Little fellas sure are cute...although
Mom and Dad look plenty scary.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.text:
That's a piece of the turtle's shell.
Guess it ended up as a wolf toy.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_01_CUT_000.text:
This shell piece might be just what
I need to unpetrify ol' Mr. Turtle.
Lemme just run it over there once quick.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
Might be something good in this cave.
I'll just take a quick peek around.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
There's all sorts of stuff stashed
away in this cave. Guess I know
who's been living here, eh?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
Hey now, these are shiny!
Wonder what they are.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
It's Mr. Bear's missing teeth!
Talk about your lucky finds right there.
I'll just take 'em to their rightful owner.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
Could be treasure inside this cave,
or could be a whole lot of nothin'.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
Looks like a pretty dangerous critter made
a home here. I could keep going, but it's
hard to imagine I'll find anything good.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
Yep. Whole lot of nothin'.
No point going any further.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_02_ROUTE2_.text:
All that just for a dead end, eh?
Talk about your wastes of time!

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.text:
Well, this sure is one strange-looking
plant. Could be carnivorous, maybe?
I've heard these—

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.text:
I know that plant didn't mean nothing by it,
but nobody enjoys being attacked straight
out of left field like that.

SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_FUNC_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_AUTO_CU.text:
Guess I gotta take extra care,
especially if I'm traveling with a bug.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
I know that thing's a plant, but it's got
a real gluttonous gleam in its...petals?
Best I keep a respectful distance.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
Gosh, looks like there's something in
its mouth already. Gonna have to get
closer if I want to grab it, though.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
Just take it easy there, slugger!
I'm not your dinner.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
Oh hey, a piece of shell!
Better take this back to Mr. Turtle.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_03_ROUTE2_.text:
Now what the heck is this? A piece of
turtle shell? Well, considering what I
risked for it, I'm not putting it back.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUT_000.text:
An empty bird's nest, eh? Oh, and we've
got some brown feathers scattered about.
Guess the chicks all flew away, maybe?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUT_000.text:
Gosh, what's a snake skin doing in
a place like this? I hear it's good luck
to put these fellas in your wallet,
so maybe I'll just give that a shot.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_EGGS_CU.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_EGGS_CU.text:
All right, that should do the trick.
'Course, the snake'll probably just
come after you again.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.text:
Well, this is your nest, yeah?
Oh, and look! Your eggs are back!

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.text: Gah! The heck are you doing!?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.text:
Kicked all the eggs outta the nest, eh?
I guess this wasn't your nest and
those weren't your eggs.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_CUCKOO_.text: Boy howdy, I messed that up good.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_OWL_CUT.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_OWL_CUT.text: Sure looks like I made someone happy.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_OWL_CUT.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_04_OWL_CUT.text:
Better give everybody a little family
time and sneak on outta here...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.text:
Maybe that nest I found and those lost
eggs both belong to Mrs. Bird here?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.text:
She seems awfully worked up, which would
make sense if her eggs got stolen.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.text:
Looks like her plumage
is grey and white.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_05_CUT_000.text:
Well, heck. Should I lead this
bird back to that nest?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_06_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_06_CUT_000.text:
This fella has a bit of a gloomy vibe,
but maybe owls are just like that?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_06_CUT_000.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_06_CUT_000.text:
Looks like it's got brown
and beige plumage.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
Look at the way that fella is brandishing
his antlers. Yeah, probably best not
to get too close here.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
Hold on though—we got a bat wing
hanging off the tip of that antler!
I better get it...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
Phew! Managed to pluck that bat wing
off the deer without getting gored.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
But Mr. Bat was missing two wings,
so I'll need one more.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_FOREST_07_ROUTE2_.text:
That's both the missing wings!
Let's get these back to Mr. Bat.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_SPIRIT_000_CUT_000_010.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_SPIRIT_000_CUT_000_010.text:
There's a weak wood spirit here.
Is that power good enough?

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_SPIRIT_000_CUT_000_011.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_SPIRIT_000_CUT_000_011.text:
There's a moderately powerful
wood spirit here. Probably about
all I can handle, honestly.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_SPIRIT_000_CUT_000_012.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_SPIRIT_000_CUT_000_012.text:
There's a strong wood spirit here.
This'll be a real tough fight...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_SPIRIT_000_CUT_000_013.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_SPIRIT_000_CUT_000_013.text:
Man alive, there's a crazy amount of power
coming from the wood spirit here!
I might not even have a chance...

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_EAR.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_GUARDIAN_FOREST_04_EAR.text: Maybe I oughta give 'em this nut.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_EA.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_03_ROUTE2_EA.text: There's a nut here. Can't believe someone would just go around wasting food like that.

SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_EA.speaker: Tsunanori_Mido
SUB_W19_EVAR_MIDO_PLAT_NEST_04_ROUTE2_EA.text: Cripes, it's carrying a seed. Maybe I can get a buncha seeds if I find its colony.
